# ShadowVoice Backend

## Install
```bash
python3 -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -e ".[dev]"
```

## Run
```bash
python -m app.main
```

The API starts on `http://127.0.0.1:8000`.

## Test
```bash
pytest
```
